snippet.title: Fishing Planet - Official Trailer | PS4
snippet.description:
Fishing Planet isn’t just another game about fishing, but a true-to-life fishing simulator that’s coming to PS4 on August 29th! The combination of stunning eye-candy graphics, superb hydro and aerodynamics, realistic tackle behavior and damage and, most importantly, fish with artificial intelligence for completely lifelike behavior bring the realistic world of fishing directly to your screen. Choose your lures, make your trophy catches, discover new possibilities and sharpen your real angling skills anywhere, anytime with your friends.

http://www.fishingplanet.com
